export function filterEmptyRanges(ranges) {
    /* **/
    var aiRanges = {}
    for (var pieceId of Object.keys(ranges)) {
        if (ranges[pieceId].length > 0) {
            aiRanges[pieceId] = ranges[pieceId]
        }
    }
    return aiRanges
}
